data.description: SHORT SALE.  OFFFER SUBMITTED TO THIRD PARTY FOR REVIEW.  Lots of character 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom, Traditional style home on just under 2 acres (1.98 acres).  Updated in 1977.  Free standing 2 car garage/shop.  Covered front porch and back patio.  36x15 family room with fireplace, wet bar and water feature.  Large living room, large kitchen, large bedrooms.  House level with Liberty and lower field level with Dew Road.  Buyer to pay $5,500 to Greenway Financial Recovery LLC for short sale negotiation fee.
